Package: cleanplots
Title: 'cleanplots' Color Scales and Theme for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Trenton D.", "Mize", email = "tmize@purdue.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Color scales and a theme for 'ggplot2' implementing the
    'cleanplots' graphing scheme by Trenton D. Mize, originally developed
    for Stata <https://www.trentonmize.com/software/cleanplots>. Designed
    for clean, publication-ready default plots of predictions and marginal
    effects. Provides discrete color and fill scales with the main and
    bar/area versions of the palette, and a theme matching the scheme's
    layout defaults.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://tdmize.github.io/cleanplots/, https://github.com/tdmize/cleanplots, https://www.trentonmize.com/software/cleanplots
BugReports: https://github.com/tdmize/cleanplots/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
